<paragraph id="8B9B36AEFF9CFFCC64E3FFC75807FDEC" blockId="4.[151,1436,1951,2014]" lastBlockId="5.[151,1436,151,213]" lastPageId="5" lastPageNumber="187" pageId="4" pageNumber="186">
Described and named as a new species by comparison with 
<taxonomicName id="4C244D2DFF9CFFCD6779FFC75AC9FAE4" authorityName="Laveran" authorityYear="1900" box="[861,1000,1987,2013]" class="Insecta" family="Culicidae" genus="Anopheles" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="186" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="coustani">
